Parents' perspectives on nusinersen treatment for children with spinal muscular 
atrophy.

van Kruijsbergen M(1), Schröder CD(1)(2), Ketelaar M(1), van der Pol WL(3), 
Cuppen I(3), van der Geest A(1)(4), Asselman FL(3), Fischer MJ(1), Visser-Meily 
JMA(1)(4), Kars MC(5).

