Assessment of the effectiveness of radiofrequency ablation as a technique for 
destroying small renal tumors in patients older than 70.

Lesnyak O(1), Stroy O(2), Banyra O(3)(4), Nikitin O(5), Grytsyna Y(6), Hayda 
I(7)(8), Chaplia M(2), Borzhievskyy A(2).

